data.description: Welcome to this charming and well maintained 3 bedroom, 1 bath Cape Cod located in Cleveland’s desirable neighborhood of West Park conveniently close to Kamm's Corner. This home boasts numerous updates while maintaining all of its original cape cod charm. You are welcomed by a spacious living room with rich natural light. The first floor has 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom, while the second floor provides a generous master bedroom with a bonus room that is perfect for an office space. The hot water tank and carpet on the main floor were updated in 2023. This home offers a fenced in backyard. Enjoy this sizeable basement that is the perfect canvas to create your own second living space. This home is in a quiet neighborhood and is completely turn-key near many conveniences such as all major highways, shopping centers, restaurants and much more! Schedule your appointment today!
